Model.Text: Tell us who's behind all this!
You tell me who's trying to sabotage my plans, and I will release you immediately.
Still don't want to talk?
Got a lot tougher, eh. You were crying your eyes out when I scarred your face a couple years ago.
I finally got Master Jahan to back me on this. Can't have you lot ruining the business!
Good, so you got guts! Bring me that!
Do you know what this is?
Master Jahan and I tore down a large chuck of the Slums for the sole purpose of manufacturing this stuff right here.
Once you take a sniff, you will become addicted. You'll do anything in order to get your hands on it.
Of course, that includes telling me everything I want to know!
Eve, are you alright?
I-I'm fine.
Let's go!
OK!
Is everything okay?
People who mess with my plans will die!
Nigel!
Eve! Eve!
I...I'm fine...
Th-The...Feather Clan?
